mplateStyles:r981673959"><span class=3D"legend-color mw-no-invert" style=3D=
"forced-color-adjust:none; background-color:lightgreen; color:black;">&nbsp=
;</span> remainder (<span class=3D"texhtml"><i>r</i></span>) as functions o=
f dividend (<span class=3D"texhtml"><i>a</i></span>), using truncated divis=
ion</figcaption></figure>
<p>Many implementations use <i>truncated division</i>, for which the quotie=
nt is defined by
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e q=3D\operatorname {trunc} \left({\frac {a}{n}}\right)}">
  <semantics>
